# NOTE: public/media/ IS committed. The screenshots and clips are the marketing site's
# proof, and keeping them in the repo means a deploy is just a build — no object store,
# no signed URLs, no second place for them to go missing. Keep clips under ~3 MB (see
# docs/MARKETING_MEDIA.md); if the total ever gets uncomfortable, move them to a CDN
# then, not pre-emptively.
